1. Bele ruže su mi omiljene. (*bele*, Subject) (White roses are my favorite.)
2. Kupila sam *bele* čarape za novogodišnju noć. (Direct object) (I bought white socks for New Year's Eve.)
3. Ona nosi *bele* cipele uz svoju haljinu. (Adjective) (She is wearing white shoes with her dress.)
4. *Bele* rukavice su idealne za hladne zimske dane. (Adjective) (White gloves are perfect for cold winter days.)
5. Kako su lepe ove *bele* zavese u sobi! (*bele*, Adjective) (These white curtains in the room are so beautiful!)
6. Sutra ćemo farbati *bele* zidove u plavo. (*bele*, Adjective) (Tomorrow we will paint the white walls blue.)
7. *Beleške* koje sam napisao pomoći će mi da naučim gradivo. (*Beleške*, Noun) (The notes I wrote down will help me learn the material.)
8. Zaboravio sam da donesem *belešku* sa sastanka. (*Belešku*, Accusative) (I forgot to bring the note from the meeting.)
9. Uvek sa sobom nosi *beleške* kako bi se organizovala. (*Beleške*, Plural noun) (She always carries notes with her to stay organized.)
10. Ovo je važna *beleška* koju morate zapamtiti. (*Beleška*, Noun) (This is an important note that you need to remember.)